---
import Layout from '~/layouts/NesthingLayout.astro';
import ResilienceCTA from '~/components/ResilienceCTA.astro';
---

<Layout metadata={{ title: '可部署的 AI 运营系统 | 服务方案' }}>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white antialiased">
    <!-- 头部：商业价值与定位 -->
    <header class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 text-center">
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-emerald-400 tracking-widest uppercase block mb-3">核心业务矩阵</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-6">双引擎部署架构</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">对内，我们通过自主流水线注入极致效率；对外，我们通过语义图谱牢牢控制搜索能见度。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-16">
      
      <!-- 主引擎：n8n 自动化线索接入 -->
      <section class="border border-[var(--color-linear-border)] bg-[var(--color-linear-card)]/20 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 relative overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[3px] bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-600"></div>
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">主引擎 (Alpha)</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">24/7 全自动线索无缝接入流水线</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
          彻底消除人工运营的低效摩擦。我们利用企业级的高级工作流框架，构建闭环式流量拦截结构——系统能够实时捕获来自 WhatsApp 等渠道的原始咨询，在 60 秒内智能完成预算门槛判定、线索自动打标，并将高净值咨询直接锁定在您的日程表上。
        </p>
        <div class="text-xs font-mono text-gray-500">// 技术栈: 模块化 Webhooks, 安全 CRM 同步, 智能 API 路由</div>
      </section>

      <!-- 辅助引擎：企业级 AI 记忆状态自愈 -->
      <section class="relative bg-slate-950 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 p-8 md:p-12 overflow-hidden group">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-indigo-500/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-center">
          <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-4">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center space-x-2 bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/30 rounded-full px-4 py-1 text-sm text-indigo-400 font-medium">
              <span>🛡️ 独家技术</span>
              <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-indigo-400 rounded-full"></span>
              <span>三层检查点</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">三层状态检查点自愈设计</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              通过将实时运行状态、客观业务事实与大模型认知意图进行刚性分离，我们的辅助引擎能够确保绝对的数据完整性。即使遭遇外部 API 崩溃或网络波动，系统也能从断点处毫秒级自动恢复，绝不丢弃任何一个运行中的高价值工作流。
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- 右侧：阶梯堆栈 -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col space-y-4 relative pl-4 border-l border-slate-800/80">
            <!-- L3 -->
            <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-950/40 to-slate-900/50 border border-purple-500/20 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm transform transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 border border-purple-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-purple-400 font-bold text-sm">L3</div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Semantic Decisions / 策略认知层</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">存储每一次 AI 行动的底层动机与战略意图，为系统的自主微调与策略自愈提供源源不断的反思动力。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- L2 -->
            <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-950/30 to-slate-900/50 border border-indigo-500/20 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm transform transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 border border-indigo-500/30 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-400 font-bold text-sm">L2</div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Source of Truth / 唯一事实数据账本</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">留存可审计、可验证的企业刚性事实与执行快照，让您的业务运作完全绝缘于大模型的“幻觉”干扰。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- L1 -->
            <div class="p-5 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-900/80 to-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 shadow-xl backdrop-blur-sm transform transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
              <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 border border-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 font-bold text-sm">L1</div>
                <div class="flex-1">
                  <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Runtime State / 瞬时运行上下文</h4>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">在单个循环中实时高效传递局部变量，任务执行完毕即刻安全释放，保持运行环境极致轻量。</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Bento 网格特性区域 -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- 存储分级 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-emerald-500/5 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-400 mb-6">⚡</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">多级冷热分流基础设施</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              高频请求指纹与规划缓存直接在<b>毫秒级快取层</b>被瞬间拦截；核心决策安全沉淀到<b>不可变事实账本</b>；而冗长的原始链路日志则自动同步至成本极低的<b>弹性对象存储舱</b>——确保主数据库永远保持轻盈与高性能响应。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex space-x-2 text-xs font-mono text-emerald-400">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 rounded">极速缓存响应</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 rounded">干净利落的架构</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 隐形接入 -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-slate-950 border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden flex flex-col justify-between">
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-blue-500/5 blur-[80px] rounded-full"></div>
          <div>
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 mb-6">👁️‍🗨️</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">主动式异步「隐形」接入引擎</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
              彻底打破笨重且极易引发封禁的传统定时轮询模式。利用事件驱动型（Push）底层蓝图配合即时指纹验证，实现对外部输入数据的无缝感知与消化，使整套架构的画布节点与连线噪点精简 50% 以上。
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex space-x-2 text-xs font-mono text-blue-400">
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/10 rounded">事件驱动流</span>
            <span class="px-2 py-1 bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/10 rounded">零延迟损耗</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- 🎯 完美的全局商业闭环整合组件，完美对齐页面宽度 -->
    <ResilienceCTA lang="zh" whatsappNumber="60128631019" />
  </main>
</Layout>

<script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
[
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "provider": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Nesthing"
    },
    "hasOfferCatalog": {
      "@type": "OfferCatalog",
      "name": "AI Systems Deployment",
      "itemListElement": [
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "itemOffered": {
            "@type": "Service",
            "name": "24/7 Autonomous Lead Ingestion Pipeline",
            "description": "Enterprise workflow automation that qualifies and routes high-intent leads into CRM frameworks within 60 seconds."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Offer",
          "itemOffered": {
            "@type": "Service",
            "name": "LLM Recommendation & Citation Injection (AEO)",
            "description": "Generative engine optimization injecting structured entity schemas to lock top recommendations across major AI search models."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": [
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How does Nesthing prevent AI memory loss and workflow downtime during execution?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Nesthing utilizes a proprietary Three-Tier State Checkpointing architecture (L1 Runtime, L2 Rigid Fact Ledger, and L3 Cognitive Layer). By strictly isolating operational states from decision intents, the system can instantly self-heal and resume workflows from the exact point of disruption without data loss."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "What infrastructure does Nesthing use to prevent primary database bloating?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "We deploy a multi-tiered split storage infrastructure. High-frequency inputs are managed via a sub-millisecond quick-cache layer, critical operational decisions are logged to an immutable core ledger, and heavy raw tracing data is automatically offloaded to an elastic object vault to keep the primary databases clean and light."
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "How does the Asynchronous Stealth Ingestion Engine reduce system latency?",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "Instead of relying on heavy, legacy scheduled cron-polling or continuous active scraping, Nesthing leverages an event-driven 'Push' framework combined with instant fingerprint matching. This approach reduces overall architectural overhead by over 50% and minimizes processing latency."
        }
      }
    ]
  }
]
</script>